AWS - Region - Availability Zone - Datacenters 
    High Availability - Multi AZ deployment

        AWS Global infrrastructure - https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/global-infrastructure/

Criteria of Region selection
    * Data Regulation 
            (Banks, Gov Org will always prefer or restriction on Local Region and DCs)
    * Latency
        AWS Latency Check (https://aws-latency-test.com/)
                            (https://clients.amazonworkspaces.com/Health.html)
    * Cost (Cost varies depends on Region wise)
    * Service Availability (Some services may not be available in some region)
            (https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/global-infrastructure/regional-product-services/)

